about:
Company Description by Thomasnet
Custom manufacturer of belts for waste, recycling, automotive, foundry, logistics, construction, food, energy, agriculture, lumber, mining and processing industries. Heavy or light duty, woven, conveyor, plastic modular, leather, elevator, round, perforated, turn and power transmission belts are offered. Mechanical fasteners, belt scrapers, chute linings, adhesives, splicing kits, urethane parts and elevator buckets are distributed.

details:
Custom manufacturer of removable thermal insulation covers for engine, agricultural and military application. Available with 1/2 in. to 2 in. insulation thickness with an operating temperature of 2100 degrees F. Features include heat retention, freeze protected and sound attenuation. Covers are available with silicone and PTFE reinforced fiberglass outer cover materials, flaps, closures and cutouts designs and outer, middle and inner layers. Prototype to large runs volume production can be done. Rush service available. On-time delivery.
